'''''The Goblin Mirror''''' is a 1992 novel by [[science fiction]] and [[fantasy]] author [[C. J. Cherryh]].  It was first published in a hardcover edition by [[Ballantine Books]] under its [[Del Rey Books]] imprint, and featured cover art by Cherryh's brother, [[David A. Cherry]].

